name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Alexander ARTIST, Petitioner

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 19th day of March, 2014, the Petition for Leave to File Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc is GRANTED. Counsel is directed to file a Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 15 days of this order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
